---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Case Study: Gudangku Native — Inventory Management">
  <section class="pt-36 pb-20 bg-carbon-canvas">
    <div class="page-container">
      <a href="/case-studies" class="font-circularxx font-regular text-caption tracking-caption text-smoke hover:text-bone-white transition-colors no-underline mb-8 inline-flex items-center gap-2">
        <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 19l-7-7 7-7"/></svg>
        Back to Case Studies
      </a>
      <p class="font-circularxx font-medium text-caption tracking-caption text-iron-gray uppercase mb-2">Inventory Management</p>
      <h1 class="font-circularxx font-w450 text-display-lg leading-display-lg tracking-display-lg text-bone-white mb-6">Digitalizing Warehouse Operations</h1>
      <p class="font-circularxx font-regular text-body-sm tracking-body-sm text-smoke max-w-2xl">How a real-time inventory system reduced data entry time by 60% and eliminated stock discrepancies.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="section-gap bg-carbon-canvas">
    <div class="page-container max-w-4xl">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-5 mb-16">
        <div class="review-card text-center">
          <div class="font-circularxx font-w450 text-heading-lg tracking-heading-lg text-bone-white mb-1">-60%</div>
          <p class="review-card-attribution">Data entry time</p>
        </div>
        <div class="review-card text-center">
          <div class="font-circularxx font-w450 text-heading-lg tracking-heading-lg text-bone-white mb-1">100%</div>
          <p class="review-card-attribution">Stock accuracy</p>
        </div>
        <div class="review-card text-center">
          <div class="font-circularxx font-w450 text-heading-lg tracking-heading-lg text-bone-white mb-1">3x</div>
          <p class="review-card-attribution">Operational efficiency</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="space-y-16 max-w-3xl">
        <div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-6">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-bone-white flex items-center justify-center shrink-0" style="border-radius: 9999px;">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-carbon-canvas" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M12 9v2m0 4h.01m-6.938 4h13.856c1.54 0 2.502-1.667 1.732-2.5L13.732 4c-.77-.833-1.964-.833-2.732 0L4.082 16.5c-.77.833.192 2.5 1.732 2.5z"/></svg>
            </div>
            <h2 class="font-circularxx font-w450 text-heading tracking-heading text-bone-white">The Problem</h2>
          </div>
          <p class="review-card-quote mb-4">The client relied on manual spreadsheet tracking for years. Key issues included:</p>
          <ul class="space-y-2 review-card-quote">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-iron-gray rounded-full mt-1.5 shrink-0"></span>Frequent stock discrepancies due to manual input errors</li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-iron-gray rounded-full mt-1.5 shrink-0"></span>Delayed shipments because stock was not tracked in real-time</li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-iron-gray rounded-full mt-1.5 shrink-0"></span>Stock reports took 2-3 days to compile</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-6">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-bone-white flex items-center justify-center shrink-0" style="border-radius: 9999px;">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-carbon-canvas" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z"/></svg>
            </div>
            <h2 class="font-circularxx font-w450 text-heading tracking-heading text-bone-white">The Solution</h2>
          </div>
          <ul class="space-y-2 review-card-quote">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-iron-gray rounded-full mt-1.5 shrink-0"></span>Real-time dashboard for instant stock monitoring</li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-iron-gray rounded-full mt-1.5 shrink-0"></span>Automated notifications for low stock levels</li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-iron-gray rounded-full mt-1.5 shrink-0"></span>Barcode scanner integration for faster data entry</li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-iron-gray rounded-full mt-1.5 shrink-0"></span>Automated reports exportable to PDF and Excel</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-6">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-bone-white flex items-center justify-center shrink-0" style="border-radius: 9999px;">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-carbon-canvas" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M13 7h8m0 0v8m0-8l-8 8-4-4-6 6"/></svg>
            </div>
            <h2 class="font-circularxx font-w450 text-heading tracking-heading text-bone-white">The Result</h2>
          </div>
          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-5 mb-8">
            <div class="review-card text-center">
              <div class="font-circularxx font-w450 text-heading-lg tracking-heading-lg text-bone-white mb-1">-60%</div>
              <p class="review-card-attribution">Data entry time</p>
            </div>
            <div class="review-card text-center">
              <div class="font-circularxx font-w450 text-heading-lg tracking-heading-lg text-bone-white mb-1">0%</div>
              <p class="review-card-attribution">Stock discrepancy rate</p>
            </div>
            <div class="review-card text-center">
              <div class="font-circularxx font-w450 text-heading-lg tracking-heading-lg text-bone-white mb-1">3x</div>
              <p class="review-card-attribution">Operational efficiency</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
